{"tid":841504,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"老實講，埋土比吾成屌打真係唔係冇原因。","createTime":"2018-09-29T14:40:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T08:34:06.000Z","uid":3874,"like":87,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"a4d6583fada601f6256e3b1570a545e3e1d46e9b","tid":841504,"uid":3874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T14:40:49.000Z","msg":"雖然吾成啲手足間唔中都會爆啲柒嘢出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，例如係反下枱、連成下一線咁。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/29/221443_0b29c931730c0dbd3a7f26bd468a91ae.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F29%2F221443_0b29c931730c0dbd3a7f26bd468a91ae.png&h=9b98a38f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過啲柒嘢十居其九都係啲學生問題，要怪都係怪城大收埋咁多on9囝。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而收分嘅嘢，學校管理層就比較難控制到，畢竟口碑嘅嘢都唔係一時三刻改變到。。。<br />\n而管理層面上柒嘅嘢，我諗咗好耐，除咗冧天花同排名造假之外都諗唔到第3單<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n反觀埋土管理層嘅柒事就一單接一單<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n首先講下民主牆，唔講咁多了，自己睇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n正式宣布 埋大成為紅底大學<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/841142\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/841142</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/29/224034_8ccad2b5232d31c5fb8410de8ce4dd0a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F29%2F224034_8ccad2b5232d31c5fb8410de8ce4dd0a.png&h=6984a9ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民主牆對開早排仲裝撚埋CCTV，製造白色恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n此外，Poly又試過因爲政治原因唔批場比SU<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/理大學生會辦論壇-嘉賓有陳浩天-校方考慮-內容及嘉賓-後拒借場地/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%83%E8%BE%A6%E8%AB%96%E5%A3%87-%E5%98%89%E8%B3%93%E6%9C%89%E9%99%B3%E6%B5%A9%E5%A4%A9-%E6%A0%A1%E6%96%B9%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE-%E5%85%A7%E5%AE%B9%E5%8F%8A%E5%98%89%E8%B3%93-%E5%BE%8C%E6%8B%92%E5%80%9F%E5%A0%B4%E5%9C%B0%2F&d=TCv67g58sYfcFSVn91Z9VV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=456a4614\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%83%E8%BE%A6%E8%AB%96%E5%A3%87-%E5%98%89%E8%B3%93%E6%9C%89%E9%99%B3%E6%B5%A9%E5%A4%A9-%E6%A0%A1%E6%96%B9%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE-%E5%85%A7%E5%AE%B9%E5%8F%8A%E5%98%89%E8%B3%93-%E5%BE%8C%E6%8B%92%E5%80%9F%E5%A0%B4%E5%9C%B0%2F&h=d7b3197d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/理大學生會辦論壇-嘉賓有陳浩天-校方考慮-內容及嘉賓-後拒借場地/</a><br />\n<br />\n除咗政治嘢，又因為某啲Staff出唔到paper，而同佢地解約，聽講個別比人炒嘅Staff都幾受學生歡迎，不過都冇情講<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/175097/理大應用數學系6教員不獲續約-好評-教員質疑系方炒人填數\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F175097%2F%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E6%87%89%E7%94%A8%E6%95%B8%E5%AD%B8%E7%B3%BB6%E6%95%99%E5%93%A1%E4%B8%8D%E7%8D%B2%E7%BA%8C%E7%B4%84-%E5%A5%BD%E8%A9%95-%E6%95%99%E5%93%A1%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E7%B3%BB%E6%96%B9%E7%82%92%E4%BA%BA%E5%A1%AB%E6%95%B8&d=TCv67g58sYfcFSVn91Z9VV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=c51c43ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/175097/理大應用數學系6教員不獲續約-好評-教員質疑系方炒人填數</a><br />\n<br />\n除此之外，仲有前學生會貪污15M，我就唔信冇學校包庇嘅話可以咁無法無天<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔怕得罪講句，城大班管理層就不停諗點樣刷數據，力爭上游。反觀Poly班管理層就搞三搞四，花咁多心機打壓學生自由，不務正業。難怪吾成吊打埋土<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c447c2d26bccaac6be7f046e83f450c395181fd7","tid":841504,"uid":3874,"like":41,"dislike":15,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T14:42:10.000Z","msg":"唔記得利申：CU仔<br />\n<br />\n（City University of Hong Kong）"},{"pid":"60bc3eed7e50a9cadaca480227f7d9a60412dcdb","tid":841504,"uid":37719,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T14:42:48.000Z","msg":"國旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f48230740a3781713776e30222877b864e6a03d","tid":841504,"uid":66099,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T14:43:18.000Z","msg":"小麗老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2891e8f62c0f50b0e2c2494a8a5eb6e652b24e69","tid":841504,"uid":81256,"like":31,"dislike":13,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T14:44:30.000Z","msg":"幾多文字都掩蓋唔到城大果陣柒味"},{"pid":"84e0081588af79604c0c1479d1cdc9e960a5bd5b","tid":841504,"uid":3874,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"60bc3eed7e50a9cadaca480227f7d9a60412dcdb","tid":841504,"uid":37719,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T14:42:48.000Z","msg":"國旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/